---
/**
 * Trzy główne audyty – 2 darmowe self-serve + 1 płatny.
 * Naprzemienny layout (lewa-prawa-lewa), każdy z dedykowanym mock UI.
 */
---

<section class="relative w-full" style="background: var(--bg);" id="audyty" aria-labelledby="audyty-title">
  <div class="content-container py-20 lg:py-28">

    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="mx-auto mb-20 max-w-3xl text-center">
      <span class="meta mb-4 inline-block">Co dostajesz</span>
      <h2
        id="audyty-title"
        class="text-ink font-display mt-2 mb-6 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.03em] sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
      >
        Dwa darmowe testy i&nbsp;jeden pełny audyt
      </h2>
      <p class="text-ink-soft text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Zacznij od sprawdzenia, jak AI widzi Twoją markę &ndash; bez logowania, bez zapłaty.
        Gdy zobaczysz wyniki, decydujesz, czy chcesz pełny raport z planem działania.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- AUDYT 1 – Brand check (free, instant) -->
    <article
      id="brand-check"
      class="border-rule bg-bg-card relative mb-10 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border p-8 sm:p-12 lg:p-16"
    >
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-24 -left-24 h-64 w-64 rounded-full"
        style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,106,46,0.16) 0%, transparent 70%);"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center lg:gap-16">

        <!-- Copy -->
        <div>
          <div class="mb-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-[color:var(--accent-edge)] bg-[color:var(--accent-soft)] px-2.5 py-1 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              Darmowe · instant
            </span>
            <span class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              01 / 03
            </span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-ink font-display mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em] sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.25rem] lg:leading-[1.1]">
            Sprawdź, co AI wie o&nbsp;Twojej marce
          </h3>
          <p class="text-ink-soft mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed sm:text-lg">
            Wpisujesz nazwę firmy. Odpytujemy ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini i&nbsp;Perplexity,
            co wiedzą o&nbsp;Twojej marce, jakie produkty kojarzą i&nbsp;czy nie mylą Cię
            z&nbsp;konkurencją. Wynik &ndash; w&nbsp;60&nbsp;sekund.
          </p>

          <ul class="text-ink-soft mb-8 space-y-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              Sentyment i&nbsp;halucynacje per model
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              Lista konkurentów, których AI poleca zamiast Ciebie
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              Luki w&nbsp;knowledge graph &ndash; co warto sprostować
            </li>
          </ul>

          <a class="btn-primary" href="/narzedzia/brand-check" aria-label="Uruchom darmowy brand check">
            Sprawdź markę &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Mock UI – brand check results per LLM -->
        <div
          class="border-rule bg-bg relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border p-6 sm:p-7"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <div class="text-ink-mute mb-4 flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase">
            <span>Brand check · podgląd</span>
            <span class="text-accent">● live</span>
          </div>

          <div class="text-ink-soft mb-3 font-mono text-xs">
            Marka: <span class="text-ink">acme.pl</span>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <!-- ChatGPT -->
            <div class="border-rule bg-bg-card rounded-lg border p-3">
              <div class="mb-1 flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-ink font-mono text-xs font-semibold">ChatGPT</span>
                <span class="text-accent font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">Zna · myli ofertę</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-ink-soft text-[11px] leading-snug">
                "Acme to polska firma SaaS oferująca CRM…" <span class="text-ink-mute">(błąd: nie CRM)</span>
              </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Claude -->
            <div class="border-rule bg-bg-card rounded-lg border p-3">
              <div class="mb-1 flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-ink font-mono text-xs font-semibold">Claude</span>
                <span class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">Brak danych</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-ink-soft text-[11px] leading-snug">
                "Nie mam aktualnych informacji o&nbsp;tej marce."
              </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Gemini -->
            <div class="border-rule bg-bg-card rounded-lg border p-3">
              <div class="mb-1 flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-ink font-mono text-xs font-semibold">Gemini</span>
                <span class="text-accent font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">Poleca konkurenta</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-ink-soft text-[11px] leading-snug">
                "W&nbsp;tej kategorii liderem jest <span class="text-ink">Konkurent X</span>…"
              </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Perplexity -->
            <div class="border-rule bg-bg-card rounded-lg border p-3">
              <div class="mb-1 flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-ink font-mono text-xs font-semibold">Perplexity</span>
                <span class="text-accent font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">Zna · neutralny</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-ink-soft text-[11px] leading-snug">
                "Acme to polska firma działająca od 2018 r." <span class="text-ink-mute">(źródło: wikipedia)</span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- AUDYT 2 – URL check (free, instant) -->
    <article
      id="url-check"
      class="border-rule bg-bg-card relative mb-10 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border p-8 sm:p-12 lg:p-16"
    >
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-24 -right-24 h-64 w-64 rounded-full"
        style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,106,46,0.16) 0%, transparent 70%);"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center lg:gap-16">

        <!-- Mock UI – URL score breakdown (LEFT this time, naprzemiennie) -->
        <div
          class="border-rule bg-bg relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border p-6 sm:p-7 lg:order-1"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <div class="text-ink-mute mb-4 flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase">
            <span>URL check · podgląd</span>
            <span class="text-accent">● live</span>
          </div>

          <div class="text-ink-soft mb-4 truncate font-mono text-xs">
            URL: <span class="text-ink">acme.pl/blog/jak-wybrac-saas</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Score -->
          <div class="mb-6 flex items-baseline gap-3">
            <div class="text-accent font-display text-6xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em]">
              43
            </div>
            <div class="text-ink-soft text-xl font-semibold">/ 100</div>
            <div class="text-ink-mute ml-2 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              Słaby wynik
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Breakdown -->
          <div class="space-y-2.5">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-soft">Front-loading (TL;DR)</span>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-1.5 w-28 rounded-full">
                  <div class="bg-accent h-full rounded-full" style="width: 78%;"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-ink w-8 text-right">78</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-soft">Schema / structured data</span>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-1.5 w-28 rounded-full">
                  <div class="bg-accent h-full rounded-full" style="width: 25%;"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-ink w-8 text-right">25</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-soft">Cytowania źródeł</span>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-1.5 w-28 rounded-full">
                  <div class="bg-accent h-full rounded-full" style="width: 12%;"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-ink w-8 text-right">12</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-soft">Statystyki / data</span>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-1.5 w-28 rounded-full">
                  <div class="bg-accent h-full rounded-full" style="width: 35%;"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-ink w-8 text-right">35</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-soft">Struktura pasaży</span>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-1.5 w-28 rounded-full">
                  <div class="bg-accent h-full rounded-full" style="width: 65%;"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-ink w-8 text-right">65</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="border-rule mt-5 border-t pt-4">
            <div class="text-ink-mute mb-1 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              Top rekomendacja
            </div>
            <p class="text-ink-soft text-[11px] leading-snug">
              Dodaj 3-5 cytowań źródeł w&nbsp;pierwszych 30% tekstu &ndash; LLM 2x częściej cytują
              treści z&nbsp;referencjami.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Copy (RIGHT) -->
        <div class="lg:order-2">
          <div class="mb-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-[color:var(--accent-edge)] bg-[color:var(--accent-soft)] px-2.5 py-1 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              Darmowe · instant
            </span>
            <span class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              02 / 03
            </span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-ink font-display mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em] sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.25rem] lg:leading-[1.1]">
            Sprawdź, czy Twój content jest cytowany przez AI
          </h3>
          <p class="text-ink-soft mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed sm:text-lg">
            Wskazujesz jeden URL. Analizujemy go pod kątem 5&nbsp;czynników, na które patrzą modele
            językowe: front-loading, schema, cytowania, statystyki, struktura pasaży. Score 0&ndash;100
            i&nbsp;konkretna lista zmian.
          </p>

          <ul class="text-ink-soft mb-8 space-y-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              Co jest źle, dlaczego LLM tego nie cytuje
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              5 priorytetowych zmian z&nbsp;szacowanym efektem
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              Bazuje na badaniach Princeton (KDD&nbsp;2024) i&nbsp;Indig&nbsp;(1.2M&nbsp;cytowań ChatGPT)
            </li>
          </ul>

          <a class="btn-primary" href="/narzedzia/url-check" aria-label="Uruchom darmowy URL check">
            Sprawdź URL &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- AUDYT 3 – Pełny audyt (paid, 3 dni) – mocniejszy orange edge, ten sam dark canvas -->
    <article
      id="pelny-audyt"
      class="bg-bg-card relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border p-8 sm:p-12 lg:p-16"
      style="border-color: var(--accent-edge); box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--accent-edge), 0 16px 48px var(--accent-glow);"
    >
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-32 -left-32 h-80 w-80 rounded-full"
        style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,106,46,0.22) 0%, transparent 70%);"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-20 -bottom-20 h-64 w-64 rounded-full"
        style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,138,79,0.14) 0%, transparent 70%);"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center lg:gap-16">

        <!-- Copy -->
        <div>
          <div class="mb-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-ink inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-rule bg-bg-elevated px-2.5 py-1 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              Płatne · 3 dni
            </span>
            <span class="text-accent font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              ★ Polecane
            </span>
            <span class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              03 / 03
            </span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-ink font-display mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em] sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.5rem] lg:leading-[1.05]">
            Pełny audyt z&nbsp;planem działania na&nbsp;90&nbsp;dni
          </h3>
          <p class="text-ink-soft mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed sm:text-lg">
            30&ndash;50 priorytetowych zapytań z&nbsp;Twojej branży × 5&nbsp;wyszukiwarek AI.
            Share of Voice vs&nbsp;konkurencja, audyt techniczny pod AI&nbsp;crawlery, mapa luk
            tematycznych i&nbsp;30/60/90-dniowa roadmapa wdrożenia.
          </p>

          <ul class="text-ink-soft mb-8 space-y-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              Raport PDF (40&ndash;60&nbsp;stron) + dashboard z&nbsp;danymi
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              Lista 20+ konkretnych zmian na stronie z&nbsp;priorytetem
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              60-min sesja prezentacji wyników z&nbsp;ekspertem ICEA
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent font-mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              Schema.org, llms.txt i&nbsp;quick-wins do wdrożenia od&nbsp;ręki
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
            <a class="btn-primary" href="/kontakt?type=full-audit" aria-label="Zamów pełny audyt widoczności AI">
              Zamów pełny audyt &rarr;
            </a>
            <span class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              od&nbsp;6&nbsp;900&nbsp;PLN
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mock UI – PDF report preview + SoV chart -->
        <div
          class="border-rule bg-bg relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border p-6 sm:p-7"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <div class="text-ink-mute mb-4 flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase">
            <span>Raport · podgląd</span>
            <span class="text-accent">● PDF · 47 stron</span>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-5">
            <div class="text-ink-mute mb-1 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              Share of Voice · acme.pl vs konkurencja
            </div>
            <div class="text-ink font-display text-3xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.02em]">
              18.4<span class="text-ink-soft text-xl">%</span>
              <span class="text-accent ml-3 font-mono text-xs">↗ +6.2pp potencjał</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Bar chart mock -->
          <div class="space-y-2.5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-24 truncate">Konkurent A</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-2 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-ink-soft h-full rounded-full" style="width: 32%;"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-12 text-right">32.1%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-24 truncate">Konkurent B</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-2 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-ink-soft h-full rounded-full" style="width: 24%;"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-12 text-right">24.7%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink w-24 truncate font-semibold">acme.pl</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-2 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-accent h-full rounded-full" style="width: 18.4%;"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-ink w-12 text-right font-semibold">18.4%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-24 truncate">Konkurent C</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-2 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-ink-soft h-full rounded-full" style="width: 14%;"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-ink-soft w-12 text-right">14.2%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <span class="text-ink-mute w-24 truncate">Pozostali</span>
              <div class="bg-bg-elevated h-2 flex-1 rounded-full">
                <div class="bg-ink-mute/40 h-full rounded-full" style="width: 10%;"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-ink-mute w-12 text-right">10.6%</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Action items -->
          <div class="border-rule mt-5 border-t pt-4">
            <div class="text-ink-mute mb-2 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider uppercase">
              Roadmapa · 23 action items
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-1.5">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px]">
                <span class="text-accent">P0</span>
                <span class="text-ink-soft truncate">Schema FAQ na 12 podstronach kategorii</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px]">
                <span class="text-accent">P0</span>
                <span class="text-ink-soft truncate">Pillar /porownanie-[marka]-vs-konkurencja</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px]">
                <span class="text-accent">P1</span>
                <span class="text-ink-soft truncate">Wikidata + Wikipedia onboarding</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-ink-mute font-mono text-[10px]">
                + 20 więcej w&nbsp;raporcie
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </article>

  </div>
</section>
